Scooby-Doo! Pirates Ahoy! (in 91 minutes Signature Edition on August 19, 2014 by 20th Century Fox Print) is a 2006 film about when the gang takes a cruise in the Bermuda Triangle and are attacked by supposed ghost pirates.

Directed by Chuck Sheetz. Written by Margaret M. Dean.

Other

[edit]

Captain Skunkbeard: Who dares enter the Bermuda Triangle? Ye have crossed paths with Captain Skunkbeard, and now ye shall pay the price!
